Рассчет эффективности rougher.output.recovery (MAE)¶

:

$$\text{$Recovery = \dfrac{C \times (F-T)}{F \times (C-T)} \times 100\% $}$$

:

  • C /;
  • F / /;
  • T /.
In [8]:
C = data_train['rougher.output.concentrate_au']
F = data_train['rougher.input.feed_au']
T = data_train['rougher.output.tail_au']
recovery = (C * (F-T)) / (F * (C - T)) * 100

Модель¶

Функция для вычисления итоговой sMAPE¶

sMAPE (. Symmetric Mean Absolute Percentage Error, ).

sMAPE :

$$\text{$sMAPE = \dfrac{1}{N}\sum_{i=1}^{N} \dfrac{|y_i - \hat y_i|}{(|y_i| + |\hat y_i|)\div 2} \times 100\% $}$$

:

  • $y_i$ i ,
  • $\hat y_i$ i, ,
  • N
  • $\sum_{i=1}^{N}$ (i 1 N)

:

  1. (rougher.output.recovery)
  2. (final.output.recovery)

:

$$\text{${}\:{sMAPE} = 25\% \times sMAPE(rougher) + 75\% \times sMAPE(final)$}$$
In [25]:
def smape(target, pred):
    smape = abs(target - pred) / ((abs(target) + abs(pred)) / 2) * 100
    smape = smape.fillna(value=0)
    smape = sum(smape) / len(smape)
    return smape

def smape_final(smape_rougher, smape_final):
    return 0.25 * smape_rougher + 0.75 * smape_final
    
smape_score = make_scorer(smape, greater_is_better=False)
